h2. 6. New Files Created

h3. 6.1 New Classes

{code:title=New Class List}
com.barclays.api.status.mgmt.schedular.model.ExecutionResults
  → Replaces org.kie.api.executor.ExecutionResults
  → Simple Map<String,Object> wrapper

com.barclays.api.status.mgmt.schedular.adapter.ExecutorServiceAdapter
  → Core adapter wrapping Quartz Scheduler
  → Provides scheduleRequest(), cancelRequest(), getQueuedRequests(),
    isQueued(), isRunning(), seedCronJob()

com.barclays.api.status.mgmt.schedular.adapter.CommandExecutorJob
  → Quartz Job implementation
  → Annotated @DisallowConcurrentExecution for multi-pod safety
  → Maps commandName → queueName → calls QSchedulerService.trigger()

com.barclays.api.status.mgmt.schedular.adapter.SchedulerStartupSeeder
  → ApplicationListener<ApplicationReadyEvent>
  → Seeds all 10 cron jobs on startup
  → Idempotent - safe on multi-pod startup

com.barclays.api.status.mgmt.schedular.util.SchedulerUtils
  → Holds @Value injected cron expressions from properties
  → Replaces old SchedulerUtils.getOlaresponseqRuntime() etc.

com.barclays.api.status.mgmt.config.QuartzConfig
  → Wires Quartz to BAMOE Oracle datasource (RPAM schema)
  → Provides SpringBeanJobFactory for @Autowired in Job classes
{code}

