h3. 6.3 Deleted Classes

{code:title=Deleted Class List - 14 Command Implementations}
OlaResponseQServiceImpl
NoInterfaceQServiceImpl
NTCHoldQServiceImpl
NGCBckServiceImpl
LogCleanUpServiceImpl
CASLSSQServiceImpl
NODEQServiceImpl
NoUploadQServiceImpl
BatchResubmitQServiceImpl
LapsedProcessServiceImpl
FailedSoftToHardServiceImpl
ApplicationExpiryProcessServiceImpl
AdvancedLogCleanUpServiceImpl
SMSRetryServiceImpl
{code}

All 14 classes had identical structure:
- Implemented Command + Reoccurring
- execute() only called QSchedulerService.trigger(queueName)
- getScheduleTime() only returned cron-based date
- Both responsibilities replaced by CommandExecutorJob + SchedulerStartupSeeder

----

h2. 7. Multi-Pod Safety Analysis

|| Concern || Old Solution || New Solution ||
| Duplicate job execution across pods | jBPM ExecutorService pessimistic DB lock on REQUESTINFO | Quartz JDBCJobStore pessimistic DB lock on QRTZ_FIRED_TRIGGERS |
| Job state loss on pod restart | REQUESTINFO persisted in Oracle | QRTZ_* tables persisted in Oracle |
| Concurrent execution of same job | jBPM handled internally | @DisallowConcurrentExecution on CommandExecutorJob |
| Pod identification | jBPM executor ID | Quartz instanceId=AUTO (unique per pod) |
| Cluster heartbeat | jBPM internal | QRTZ_SCHEDULER_STATE table |
| BPMN timer duplication | Was a known issue in BAMOE 8 | Not applicable - Quartz is external to BPMN runtime |

----

h2. 8. UI Behaviour - Unchanged

The complete UI contract is preserved:

|| UI Action || Old Behaviour || New Behaviour ||
| Page load - scheduler table | getRoboticQList() returns [{queueName: time}] | Identical format returned |
| Queue list dropdown | From robotic.queue.list property | Unchanged - same property |
| Action ON + datetime + submit | Reschedules queue to new time | Same result via Quartz SimpleTrigger |
| Action OFF + submit | Cancels scheduled run | Same result via Quartz unschedule/pause |
| Success message | "OlaResponseQ Has Been Rescheduled At..." | Identical message |
| Scheduler table refresh | Shows updated time | Shows updated Quartz next fire time |

----

